---
import { BASE, GH_URL } from '../consts';
---
<section class="bot">
  <div class="container bot-inner">
    <div class="bot-text">
      <header>
        <h2>There's a bot, too.</h2>
        <p class="lead">
          Run the same pipeline as a self-hosted Telegram bot.
          Forward a voice message, a PDF, a YouTube link, a stranger's
          <code>t.me/</code> post, or that suspicious file someone
          just sent you — get a Markdown summary back as a document,
          with cost and timing in the caption.
        </p>
      </header>

      <ul class="points">
        <li>
          <strong>Voice & video.</strong>
          Drop a 12-minute voice or a 45-minute recorded meeting — get a TL;DR in roughly the time it takes to put your phone down.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Anything weird.</strong>
          Forward suspicious links, long PDFs, or channel posts you'd rather not read. The bot reads them for you and replies with the gist.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Single-user, your hardware.</strong>
          Allowlisted to one Telegram ID (yours). Runs on your laptop or a $5 VM via docker-compose.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="ctas">
        <a href={`${BASE}/docs/bot/`} class="btn btn-primary">
          Bot guide
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href={`${GH_URL}/blob/main/docs/bot-vm-deploy.md`} class="btn btn-ghost" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
          Deploy on a VM
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bot-frame">
      <img
        src={`${BASE}/bot.jpg`}
        alt="The unread Telegram bot replying to a forwarded voice message with a TL;DR and attaching a Markdown report as a document."
        loading="lazy"
        width="603"
        height="1228"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bot {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .bot-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .bot-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
  }

  header { margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }
  .lead {
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 56ch;
  }
  .lead code {
    background: var(--bg-code);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding: 0.1em 0.4em;
    font-size: 0.88em;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .points {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 1.6rem;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  .points li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .points li::before {
    content: "›";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .points strong { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 700; }

  .ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .bot-frame {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .bot-frame img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    width: min(360px, 100%);
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    background: var(--bg-elev);
  }
</style>
